  ## 3. **Rust**
  - **Main Use Cases**: Systems programming, embedded systems, 
  performance-critical applications, blockchain/infrastructure tools
  - **Why Popular**: Memory safety without garbage collection, zero-cost 
  abstractions, strong type system, growing adoption in infrastructure projects
  
